Global Batteries & Appliances





Since 1906, providing premium products at a value price is the way we've done business. The Rayovac brand is more than just batteries. We also offer a wide variety of products including: virtually-indestructible lights, the world's longest lasting hearing aid batteries and innovative portable power solutions. Trust Rayovac for all your power needs.
Visit us at: www.rayovac.com



You need flexibility and independence? Then you live a lifestyle our products support. Whether you have a digital camera, MP3 player or Gameboy (TM), VARTA Consumer Batteries delivers precisely the right energy.
Visit us at: www.varta-consumer.com




For shaving and grooming needs or creating today’s new hair style, Remington® products keep you looking your best for less.  Remington offers a wide variety of innovative products including: hair dryers, flat irons/straighteners, rotary and foil electric shavers, personal groomers, mustache and beard groomers, and haircut kits.
Visit us at: www.remingtonproducts.com



The Black & Decker® Home brand is built on quality, durability and value. Our appliances are designed to simplify life’s daily tasks through a combination of durability, performance and practical convenience. For over 50 years, we have been a proven leader in products used throughout your home – from irons to toaster ovens, coffeemakers to can openers.
Visit us at: www.blackanddeckerappliances.com




As the groundbreakers of the indoor grilling category—and with over ten years as industry leaders—George Foreman Cooking understands better than anyone the innovative technology you want in order to cook the healthy, delicious food you and your family love.
Visit us at: www.georgeforemancooking.com



Russell Hobbs has been synonymous with life in the kitchen for over 50 years. Known, owned and proudly on display in millions of homes across the UK, Russell Hobbs’ has forged a reputation for timeless, stylish kitchen appliances.




The Juiceman® brand is built on the simple idea that incorporating fresh fruits and vegetables into your daily diet can help you feel better and have more energy as you maintain your active, healthy lifestyle.
Visit us at: www.juiceman.com



With almost a decade of leadership in helping families enjoy fresh baked bread at home, bread and baking are our passion. We strive to provide users with quality products, useful features and new innovations that make home baking fun, easy and exciting. 
Visit us at: www.breadman.com




Farberware® home appliances – a timeless brand built on impeccable design and uncompromising durability – is giving consumers a whole new reason to believe that the best meals are the ones they make right in their own kitchen.




As an icon in American home appliance heritage, the Toastmaster® name is one you can trust to deliver the features you need at a price you can afford. We offer a full line of products, from can openers and choppers to coffeemakers, toaster ovens and so much more!















