Global Pet Supplies





For more than 40 years, Marineland® has been committed to fishkeeping success. By applying biological science, advanced engineering and imagination to fishkeeping, the Marineland brand continues to be the leader in innovative aquatic environments, equipment and kits – allowing hobbyists to create the ultimate freshwater, marine and reef aquariums.
Visit us at: www.marineland.com



Life begins in the ocean. And the life of your marine aquarium begins with Instant Ocean®, the only synthetic sea salt backed by more than 40 years of research and innovation. Our name is trusted by thousands, from research institutions and marine adventure parks to longtime hobbyists and first-time aquarium owners.
Visit us at: www.instantocean.com



For over 50 years, fishkeeping enthusiasts have looked to the Tetra® name for products and solutions that add ease and beauty to their home. Whether you’re an experienced hobbyist or just starting out, Tetra® has everything you need – from a large variety of quality fish food and innovative equipment to test kits and décor.
Visit us at: www.tetra-fish.com




FURminator® continues to raise the bar with innovative, proprietary deShedding solutions. FURminator's lineup of deShedding tools, grooming tools, hair care products, bathing and hygiene solutions broadens and enhances the FURminator® deShedding experience for pet parents and their pets. Simply put, there is no pet care solution on the market like the FURminator product line.
Visit us at: www.furminator.com



Dingo® brand's patented meat and rawhide combination delivers healthy and delicious chews to promote clean teeth and gums. This premium rawhide chew offers an extensive line of irresistible products.
Visit us at: www.dingobrand.com



For over 25 years Nature’s Miracle® has offered consumers innovative problem specific solutions that address major pet stain and odor removing needs. The brand has expanded beyond the original Stain & Odor formula, branching out to training aids, cat litter, disinfectants and other products.
Visit us at: www.natures-miracle.com




Perfect Coat ® offers a full line of grooming preparations including shampoos and conditioners, as well as sprays, wipes and deShedding tools for quick between-bath refreshing. Our extensive assortment of products is formulated with the highest quality ingredients to make grooming at home a happy, healthy experience for pet and owner.



Lazy Pet® is an established pet bedding and accessory brand serving pet retailers for over 30 years. The brand is respected for high quality materials and workmanship, and innovative design. Products include Lazy Pet®, our popular bedding line of Loungers®, Poop Patrol®, Malibu Pet Products®, Kitty Condo, Action Scratcher®, Kitty Cradle®, Sof-Bed®, and Kitty Kubbyhole®.



ProSense® is a premium healthcare and grooming brand that offers a wide variety of products that work to deliver in depth information and better health for your pet. 
Visit us at: www.prosensepet.com





Excel® Healthcare products are scientifically formulated and use the highest quality ingredients to offer comprehensive solutions for all pet health & wellness needs including; vitamins, joint care, skin and coat and remedies.



The N2N™ product line is designed for pet parents and offers premium style, features and design, at a cost competitive price. Products consist of Port-A-Crate® collapsible fabric crates, Pethouse™ plastic pet carriers, Pet Retreat™ with Calm-Quil™ plastic pet kennels and Poop Patrol® Pet Waste Products. Available at Pet Specialty retailers.



Cats Crave Kookamunga! From Krayzee Kitty™ Catnip, interactive Catnip bubbles, and satisfying treats these premium products are sure to entertain and delight.




Wild Harvest™ delivers a great taste and provides advanced nutrition in every blend that birds and small animals enjoy and need to live a healthy life.



One Earth® premium foods are made of only all-natural, wholesome ingredients to provide pets with optimum healthy-balanced nutrition.



The WonderBox® licensed product line consists of disposable pet litter boxes that are made from 100% biodegradable, landfill safe, non-toxic paper pulp. The patented WonderBox® eliminates cat waste odors, extends litter life and is easy to use and convenient. Recommended by America’s top breeders and veterinarians. Made in the U.S.A.




eCOTRITION™ essential blends offer a nutritionally fortified mix of fresh ingredients scientifically formulated to help birds and small animals flourish. With fresh ingredients hand selected through field research and fortified nutrition, eCOTRITION™ Essential Blend provides everything your bird needs to flourish.
Visit us at: www.ecotrition.com



NOZTONOZ® pet products seek to outperform current industry standards. Each product represents a well thought out, well-researched idea to provide consumers with innovative solutions that improve the care and comfort of their pet. The NOZTONOZ product line consists of doghouses, Sof-Krate™ collapsible fabric crates, plastic pet carriers and pet waste clean-up products. Available at Pet Specialty retailers.



The PETNATION® brand offers innovative products with practical features and functionality. Products are available at national retailers and club stores. The product line includes insulated plastic dog houses, Port-A-Crate®, No Trace™, Night Glow collars and leashes, Port-A-Pen®, and Port-a-Bed®.




Healthy Hide - Spectrum Brands is committed to providing premium products which are formulated from superior ingredients and processed under strict, food-grade guidelines. We developed the HEALTHY-HIDE® brand with our commitment to excellence in mind: it's the brand you can trust to provide the highest quality rawhide products your dog will enjoy.



Digest-eeze - Spectrum Brands is committed to providing premium products that are formulated from superior ingredients and processed under strict, food-grade guidelines. We developed DIGEST-EEZE™ with this commitment: it's the brand you can trust to provide the most advanced, highly digestible rawhide products your dog can enjoy throughout every stage of life.




                Littermaid® cat products work to provide total litter solutions that use only the highest quality litter. The Littermaid® product line strives to help make your home environment comfortable, clean, and fresh – so you spend less time worrying about the litter box and more time loving your cat! The Littermaid® brand is committed to provide practical innovations in litter boxes and other feline care products that help ensure your cat's happiness, healthiness, and best possible indoor environment.
		    













