Spectrum Brands

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc.





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: SPB


Industry
Electric Housewares Mfg
Artificial Plants Mfg
Battery Mfg
Pesticide Mfg
Lighting Equipment Mfg


Predecessor
Rayovac Corporation


Founded
January 17, 1906; 111 years ago (1906-01-17) (as French Battery Company)
Madison, Wisconsin, U.S.


